The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | Good Morning
                                                                                                                         3                                                                                      Good Morning
      Hello It's Monday , September 6 , 2010                    
	Roads to avoid    JL Nehru Road, RR Avenue, Mayo Road, SN Banerjee Road, Esplanade Row (East) and Lenin Sarani in view of a Congress meeting at Shahid Minar around 12.30pm.    
	Cricket    The Telegraph Corporate Indoor Cricket Tournament at Space Circle Club, 7pm-9pm.    
	Exhibition    Computex 2010, an exhibition of computers, peripherals and office products, at Ice Skating Rink, 11am to 8pm.    
	Dance    Ahan 2010, dance recital by members of Srijati, at Kalakunj, 6pm.    
	In focus    Lessons in Life Lessons in Love, a photography exhibition on Mother Teresa, at Oxford Bookstore, 10am to 9pm.    
	Art watch    No Content Worries, an exhibition, at Aakriti Art Gallery, noon to 7pm.    A sculpture show by Tapan Kumar Das and Sunanda Das at Academy of Fine Arts (North Gallery), 3pm to 8pm.    Confabulations, an exhibition by Mahesh Baliga, at Galerie 88, 28B Shakespeare Sarani, 2pm to 7pm.                                                                                                                                                  
